casebody.data:
No. 596. No. 44,

Misc.

Wright v. Johnston, Warden. Wright v. Johnston, Warden. January 6, 1947. Petitioner pro se. Acting Solicitor General Washington, Robert S. Erdahl and Sheldon E. Bernstein for respondent.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the Circuit Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit; and

On motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus.

The motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus is denied. The petition for writ of certiorari is also denied.
